PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746038
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,FWhite-tailed eagles have a wingspan of
OL,7,Fup to 2.5 metres and were once
OL,8,Fwidespread across England.
OL,10,FHuman persecution caused their
OL,11,Fextinction, with the last pair
OL,12,Fbreeding in southern England in 1780.
OL,14,FAlso known as sea eagles, the species
OL,15,Fis typically found along coastlines
OL,16,Fand large bodies of open water.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746038
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,FThe project to reintroduce them, led
OL,7,Fby Forestry England and the Roy Dennis
OL,8,FWildlife Foundation, will add to
OL,9,Fexisting releases on the Isle of Wight
OL,10,Fthat began in 2019.
OL,12,FMore eagles will be introduced there,
OL,13,Fand on Exmoor, this summer.
OL,15,FAll of the released birds are fitted
OL,16,Fwith satellite tags so that the
OL,17,Fproject team can track their location
OL,18,Fand study their progress.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746038
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,FIt's hoped they will boost the number
OL,7,Fof birds already in the wild and
OL,8,Fexpand their breeding range into South
OL,9,FWest England.
OL,11,FExmoor was chosen as an additional
OL,12,Flocation after tracking data from the
OL,13,Freleased birds showed the area had
OL,14,Fbeen frequently visited by several of
OL,15,Fthem and provided suitable habitat.
OL,17,FIt is known that the species formerly
OL,18,Fbred along the Exmoor coastline.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
