OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,FTo date, 45 young white-tailed eagles
OL,7,Fhave been released from the project's
OL,8,Fbase on the Isle of Wight.
OL,10,FFour pairs of birds have bonded and
OL,11,Fsuccessfully formed territories along
OL,12,Fthe south coast.
OL,14,FThe first pair to successfully breed
OL,15,Fdid so in 2023, fledging the first
OL,16,Fchick to be born in the wild in
OL,17,FEngland for over 240 years. Since
OL,18,Fthen, a further five have been born in
OL,19,Fthe wild.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
