OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,FRoy Dennis OBE, Founder of the Roy
OL,7,FDennis Wildlife Foundation, said:
OL,8,F"White-tailed eagles were once a
OL,9,Fcommon sight in England but were lost
OL,10,Fcenturies ago.
OL,12,F"This project is reversing that
OL,13,Fsituation, and I am delighted that we
OL,14,Fwill be able to release additional
OL,15,Fbirds this year and boost their
OL,16,Fnumbers in the wild.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,F"It is exciting to be able to play a
OL,7,Fpart in restoring these birds back to
OL,8,Ftheir former home, and to see how well
OL,9,Fthey are fitting into the English
OL,10,Flandscape.
OL,12,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,13,Fa range of organisations as we enter
OL,14,Fthis next phase of this exciting
OL,15,Fproject."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,FStephen Egerton-Read, white-tailed
OL,7,Feagle project manager at Forestry
OL,8,FEngland, said: "Returning lost species
OL,9,Flike the white-tailed eagle is a key
OL,10,Fpart of restoring biodiversity and
OL,11,Fsupporting nature recovery.
OL,13,F"Seven years on from the start of this
OL,14,Fproject these birds have begun to
OL,15,Fsuccessfully return to the English
OL,16,Flandscape - forming pairs,
OL,17,Festablishing territories and breeding.
OL,26,@pD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
