OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,F"Adding additional releases at Exmoor
OL,7,Fwill help to boost their numbers and
OL,8,Fcontinue their spread across southern
OL,9,FEngland. We hope that in years to come
OL,10,Fthese iconic birds will become a much
OL,11,Fmore common sight."
OL,13,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,14,Fsaid: "The return of whitetailed
OL,15,Feagles to Exmoor is a powerful example
OL,16,Fof this government's commitment to
OL,17,Freversing the decline of nature and
OL,18,Fprotecting it for generations to come.
OL,26,@sD@SO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
