PN,43410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,F"As part of our new 'Wild Again'
OL,7,Fcampaign, we are investing #90 million
OL,8,Finto species recovery, marking the
OL,9,Flargest ever government investment to
OL,10,Fdirectly support threatened wildlife."
OL,12,FAli Hawkins, Senior Ecologist with
OL,13,FExmoor National Park Authority, said:
OL,14,F"Exmoor, with its long expanse of
OL,15,Fcoastal woodland, provides some
OL,16,Famazing habitat for White-tailed
OL,17,FEagles, otherwise known as Sea Eagles.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778746039
OL,3,CWhite-tailed eagles to be released on
OL,4,CExmoor to boost numbers in the wild
OL,6,F"Their reintroduction to the National
OL,7,FPark is an exciting next step in
OL,8,Fdelivering more for nature recovery
OL,9,Fand we'd like to thank everyone
OL,10,Fconnected to the project.
OL,12,F"We are committed to continuing to
OL,13,Fwork with farmers and other
OL,14,Fstakeholders, to support them in
OL,15,Fadapting to this species fledging on
OL,16,FExmoor once again. We hope that people
OL,17,Fwill be lucky enough to see one of
OL,18,Fthese incredible birds in the coming
OL,19,Fyears."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
